---
title: Verdict Publication — Observation Streams to Consumer API
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant API as Consumer API
    participant USER as Analyst / Operator

    Note over ORC,USER: Precondition: synthesizer STOP received.<br/>Run status = SYNTHESIZED.<br/>No edge adapter needed — observations are already JSON.

    ORC->>ORC: detect SYNTHESIZED state<br/>all 10 agents complete

    ORC->>API: notify run_complete({<br/>  run_id: "claim-4821-run-003"<br/>})

    API->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:* - +<br/>read all observations from all 10 agent streams

    API->>API: filter F and C status observations<br/>apply DetermineOBXResolution per code<br/>(select latest F or C as authoritative)

    API->>API: construct verdict response<br/>{<br/>  run_id, claim_id, claim_text,<br/>  verdict, confidence_score, narrative,<br/>  coverage: {left, center, right},<br/>  blindspot_score, blindspot_direction,<br/>  claimreview_match, claimreview_verdict,<br/>  domain_evidence_alignment,<br/>  synthesis_signal_count,<br/>  generated_at<br/>}

    API->>API: validate response schema<br/>assert required fields present<br/>assert confidence_score in [0.0, 1.0]<br/>assert verdict in controlled vocabulary

    alt schema validation passes
        API->>API: persist verdict<br/>update run status → PUBLISHED

        Note over API,USER: Verdict is now queryable by consumers.

        USER->>API: GET /verdicts/{verdict_id}
        API-->>USER: 200 OK<br/>{verdict JSON}

        USER->>API: GET /audit/{run_id}/observations
        API->>REDIS: XRANGE all streams for run_id
        API-->>USER: 200 OK<br/>{full observation log — all P/F/C/X entries}

    else schema validation fails
        API->>API: log validation error<br/>run remains SYNTHESIZED (not PUBLISHED)

        Note over ORC: Orchestrator detects publication failure.<br/>Escalates to run error log.<br/>Schema failure requires investigation.
    end
